<plot>This made-for-video documentary treats action film fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of Mission Impossible 2, the sequel to the hit film inspired by the popular 70's TV spy series. Features interviews with John Woo, Tom Cruise, and other members of the cast and crew of the film who share their experiences from working on the project, as well as discuss the special efforts that went into creating the finished product.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063775</url></doc>
